.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE_LISTFORWARDS_FEE_KURTOSIS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-listforwards-fee-kurtosis \- FEAT-2819 kurtosis of forward fees from settled forwards
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-listforwards-fee-kurtosis
.SH DESCRIPTION
Computes the kurtosis of forward fees from settled forwards for the lightning CLI (FEAT-2819).
.PP
Output: JSON object with key \fBfee_kurtosis\fR and \fBcount\fR.
Returns \fBnull\fR when fewer than the required minimum samples are available.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning (1)
